msgid "Architecture Decision Records"
msgstr "架构决策记录"

#: ../../adr/index.md:5 ea12f43edaf24813a8826cf6941a7f85
msgid ""
"Use ADRs to capture the reasoning behind meaningful architectural "
"choices, especially when the trade-offs are not obvious from the code "
"alone."
msgstr ""
"使用 ADR 来记录重要架构选择背后的原因，尤其是在仅从代码本身无法直接看出权衡取舍时。"

